• Taɛrabt tafuṣḥit: 270 id mlyun|Tawlaft azwl=''Alɛarabya'' ittyuran s [[Agmmay Aɛrab|ugmmay aɛrab]].|Tawlaft=Arabic_albayancalligraphy.svg|Tunṣibt=27 tmazirt|Takarda azwl=S uzgzaw, idɣarn nna ɣ ttuysawal tutlayt taɛrabt|Χρῶμα=#faecc8}}'''Taεṛabt''' nɣ '''Taserɣint''' (s tεrabt : الْعَرَبيّة, ''al εarabiyya'' nɣd عَرَبيْ, ''εarabī,'' s [[tamaziɣt]] n zikk : Tasrɣint<ref>https://www.academia.edu/1702492/%C3%89tudes_sur_le_Kit%C3%A2b_al_Barbariya_manuscrit_dun_texte_ibadite_m%C3%A9di%C3%A9val_</ref><ref>https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28665841</ref>) tga tutlayt nna s sawaln iεrabn, tga yat tutlayt [[Tutlayin tifrusyawiyin|tifrusyawit]]. Tkka-d taεrabt [[tutlayin tisamiyin]] zund ukan [[Tutlayt Taɛibrit|Taεibrit]] nɣ [[Tafiniqit]] n zik, nttat ay-gan tamzwarut gisnt ɣ wuṭṭun n imssiwln, Ar tinin mas-d illa ḥaqqan gr 315 mlyun d 375 mlyun n middn ar sis sawaln.

Tuckad tutlayt '''Taɛṛabt''' zɣ [[Tazunegzirt taɛṛabt]]. Ɣ tasut tiss 7 tga-d Taɛṛabt tutlayt n [[Lqʷran|lqquran]] ( Awal n rbbi ) d [[Lislam]] .

Tga Taεṛabt tutlayt tunṣibt ɣ 27 n tmizar tga ula tutlayt taɣlnawt ɣ [[Mali]], [[Sinigal]], d [[Ṣumal|Sumal]]. Tutlayt taεṛabt tettyura s ugmmay aεrab, tirra nns gi-s 28 iskkiln yttwarun zɣ ufasi ar uzlmaḍ. Teṭṭaf kigan n tantalyin, mqqar kand tantaliyin ad tutlayt taεṛabt ur aɣ bahra trmasn ingratsn, amdya : taεṛabt alubnani ur iẓḍar ay-rms taεṛabt tamrrukit. 

Nẓḍar ad nbḍu gr sin n timdyazin : tamdyazt n dat lislam, tamdyazt n dffir lislam, qarn-as s tεrabt "tajahilit".

== Tutlayt tunṣibt ==
Taɛrabt tafuṣḥit tga tutlayt tunṣibt ɣ 25 tmizar, ɣayd as-tt yujjan tga tutlayt tiss kraḍt tḍfar [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tafransist]] d [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tanglizt]] 

* Tmizar n iɛrabn : [[Tagldit Tasaɛudit|Saɛudya]], Baḥrayn, Juzur n Lqumur, Djibuti, Timizar iɛrabn imunn, lɛiraq, Urdun, Kuwit, Lubnan, Ɛuman, Filiṣṭin, Qatar, Somalya, Sudan, Surya, Yaman ;
* Tmizar n [[Tafriqt n ugafa|tfriqt n ugafa]] : [[Dzayr]], [[Miṣra]], [[Lmɣrib]], [[Muritanya]], [[Tuns]], [[Libya]] ;
* Tmizar yaḍn zund Irytri, Tcad ;

Tutlayt tunṣibt n tmazirt n [[Malṭa]], tutlayt tamalṭit, tga yat zɣ tantliwin n tutlayt taɛrabt.

== Amzruy ==
Taɛrabt tga tutlayt tasamit. Urtettuysawal Taɛrabt tafusḥit ɣ wass-ad walaynni llan sul ilsawn n taɛrabt ɣ timizar n agmud anammas n tafriqt n ugafa. 

